---
import ServiceLayout from "../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro";
const area = 'Mansfield';
const phoneNumber = '01632 325 123';
const serviceDetails = {
  title: `Mobile Tyre Repair in ${area} | Tyre Emergency Ltd`,
  description: `Fast and reliable mobile tyre repair service in ${area}. We'll get you back on the road quickly.`,
  heading: `Mobile Tyre Repair in ${area}`,
  tagline: "Flat Tyre? We'll Come to You Today and Fix It!",
};
---

<ServiceLayout {...serviceDetails} phoneNumber={phoneNumber}>
  <h1 class="fw-bold mb-3">{serviceDetails.heading}</h1>
  <p>
    Got a flat tyre? Don’t let it ruin your day. Our mobile tyre repair team in {area} is here to help, whether you’re at home, work, or stranded on the roadside.
  </p>
  <p>
    We pride ourselves on our speedy response times—most customers see us within the hour. With expert fitters and fully equipped vehicles, we’ll have you back on the road in no time.
  </p>
  <h2 class="fw-bold">Why Choose Us?</h2>
  <p>
    Emergencies don’t wait for convenient times. That’s why we’re available seven days a week to assist you with tyre issues, from punctures to flat tyres. Whether it’s a pothole mishap or a stray nail, we’ve got you covered.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our friendly, professional team understands the importance of getting you moving again quickly and safely.
  </p>

  <h2 class="fw-bold">How It Works</h2>
  <p>
    Call us, share your location, and we’ll handle the rest. Our team brings everything needed to repair or replace your tyre on the spot.
  </p>
  <p>
    Not sure if your tyre can be repaired? Don’t worry—we’ll assess the damage and recommend the best solution to get you back on track.
  </p>

  <h2 class="fw-bold">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>
    Don’t wait around with a flat tyre. Give us a call today at <a href={`tel:${phoneNumber}`} class="link-danger">{phoneNumber}</a>, and let us take the stress out of tyre trouble.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
